synopsis.text: After a shift at Maid Latte leaves Misaki Ayuzawa with a torn maid uniform, she seeks her mother's help to mend it. But her younger sister, Suzuna, steps in, expressing curiosity to try on the outfit, much to Misaki's dismay. As Misaki juggles to manage her sister's newfound interest and prevent any awkward moments, she finds herself in a whirlwind of unforeseen visitors at her home, turning her ordinary day into an unpredictable adventure!
